A group of Greek farmers gathered in
Tripoli, southern  Greece , to protest the governmentâ€™s
agricultural insurance costs, Athens News Agency reported.  The farmers met outside the offices of the Greek
Agricultural Insurance Agency to protest against the cost of
insuring agricultural products, the state-run News agency
reported, citing secretary of Pan-Hellenic Agricultural
